*pygments_rb-0.6.2 (29 Jan 2015)

  29 Jan 2015; Manuel Rüger <mrueg@gentoo.org> +pygments_rb-0.6.2.ebuild:
  Version bump.

  15 Nov 2014; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> pygments_rb-0.6.0-r2.ebuild:
  Avoid unneeded dependency on git, fixing bug 529226.

*pygments_rb-0.6.0-r2 (10 Sep 2014)

  10 Sep 2014; Manuel Rüger <mrueg@gentoo.org> +pygments_rb-0.6.0-r2.ebuild,
  -pygments_rb-0.6.0-r1.ebuild:
  Use correct gemspec.

*pygments_rb-0.6.0-r1 (02 Sep 2014)

  02 Sep 2014; Manuel Rüger <mrueg@gentoo.org> +pygments_rb-0.6.0-r1.ebuild,
  -pygments_rb-0.5.4.ebuild, -pygments_rb-0.6.0.ebuild:
  Add ruby21 target. Cleanup old.

  15 Aug 2014; Manuel Rüger <mrueg@gentoo.org> pygments_rb-0.6.0.ebuild:
  Restrict yajl-ruby dependency to =1.1*.

  16 Jul 2014; Manuel Rüger <mrueg@gentoo.org> pygments_rb-0.6.0.ebuild:
  Add ruby20 support. Remove python 2.6 support.

*pygments_rb-0.6.0 (28 Jun 2014)

  28 Jun 2014; Manuel Rüger <mrueg@gentoo.org> +pygments_rb-0.6.0.ebuild:
  Version bump.

